<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4677189>
    dc:description "Figures 1–3. (1) Occurrence records of Australian Ozeoura (then Baeoura), as of December 2017. (2, 3) Habitats of Ozeoura spp.; (2) O. convoluta, Big River, Glen Valley Victoria; (3) O. tonnoiri, Bakers Creek, Reefton Victoria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4677189/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

